{
  "stem": "25651.12",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the SS were talking about it even, I mean, not to me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you know, I was with these men of the Kleiderkammer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were informed prisoners because they had the run of the camp [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] through the work of the Kleiderkammer, the clothing department.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 11 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Galen comes to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he says, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] can you get yourself an errand to go to the Frauenlager and talk to the people in this road, the C road between C and D?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And talk to the people who are sitting next to the wire over the [NON-ENGLISH] lager on the sidings.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Tell them they're going to die.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They're waiting for the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And tell them that when they hear an explosion to throw themselves en masse on the barbed wire and to fell the barbed wire-- you know, make it-- make it fall.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because our pals will then join us from the [NON-ENGLISH], the rest of the Sonderkommando.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So I talked to Harting.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he arranged it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I get an order to go to the Frauenlager and talk to a Blockalteste on block so-and-so that women's detail is to report to Kanada such and such and such and such.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I have proper orders, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, I didn't have orders.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that's how it was made up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we weren't allowed to talk to the prisoners on the ramp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I already got beaten once to do it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I knew something was up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I start talking to people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And you see, I'm well-dressed like a bellhop [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] with this thing.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
